{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"SMTP","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/SMTP","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>SMTP</strong>（Simple Mail Transfer Protocol，简单邮件传输协议）是用于发送的邮件的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Protocol\">协议</a>。类似于<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/POP\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">POP3 (en-US)</a>和<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/NNTP\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">NNTP (en-US)</a>，它是一个<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/State_machine\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">状态机 (en-US)</a>驱动的协议</p>\n<p>该协议相对简单。最复杂的部分在于添加支持不同的验证机制（<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Generic_Security_Services_Application_Program_Interface\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">GSSAPI</a>， <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CRAM-MD5\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CRAM-MD5</a>，<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NTLM\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">NTLM</a>，MSN，AUTH LOGIN，AUTH PLAIN 等），处理错误响应以及在验证机制错误时进行状态回退（如服务器声明其支持某种机制但其实并不）。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary\">术语表</a>\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/NNTP\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">NNTP (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/POP\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">POP3 (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Protocol\">协议</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/State_machine\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">状态机 (en-US)</a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li>维基百科\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/SMTP\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">SMTP</a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"SMTP（Simple Mail Transfer Protocol，简单邮件传输协议）是用于发送的邮件的协议。类似于POP3 (en-US)和NNTP (en-US)，它是一个状态机 (en-US)驱动的协议","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"SMTP","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"SMTP","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"SMTP","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"SMTP","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"SMTP","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/smtp","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/smtp/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/SMTP","title":"SMTP"}],"pageTitle":"SMTP - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}